Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:48.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い事　揺れる音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:51.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そっとひそめる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:59.11,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}頬のそばで舞う雪達…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:01:06.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}たくさんの後悔　過去を結ぶ笑顔たち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:09.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風のささやき
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:12.56,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}触れて溶ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:20.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冬空の淋しさを重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:28.95,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}優しさの瞳越えて　今
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:36.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伝えたいメロディ　指差した一番星光る空に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:44.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描き集めた未来　かじかんだ指の隙間通る星座たち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:52.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Ah　この場所から見た景色　叶えたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:58.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約束ね
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:48.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中的願望  搖曳的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:51.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悄悄隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:59.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}讓飛雪滑過臉頰…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:01:06.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揮之不去的後悔  緊繫過去的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:09.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風的細語
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:12.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一觸即散
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:20.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寒空中夾雜著寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:28.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}越過了眼中的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:36.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在想給你的旋律  遙指著初星的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:44.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}天空拼湊出的未來  手指間露出的星座
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:52.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊  想要實現在此看見的景色…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:58.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約定好了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:22.56,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}揺れる水面　その深くに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:26.22,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}青い宇宙映ってたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:29.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来…そしてまた散っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.17,0:22:33.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}季節覚えている？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:41.44,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私たちは運命紡ぎながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.95,0:22:46.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その糸がどこまで続いてくのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:50.49,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}知らないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:51.42,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(ただそこに)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:54.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}inspiration　喜びとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:58.27,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}言葉を分かち合うたび
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.53,0:23:02.08,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ああいつか終わりの日が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:05.84,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そう感じさせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:09.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}initialize　その扉を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:13.36,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}開ける時が来るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:17.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}綺麗な時を閉じ込めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:20.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}湖に沈めたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:24.71,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけど私平気だよと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.93,0:23:30.35,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}星の便りに綴る
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:22.56,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在漣漪的水面深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:26.22,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}照映著蔚藍的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:29.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未來又將飄零而去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.17,0:22:33.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}唯此季節長存心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:41.44,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們編織命運之絲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.95,0:22:46.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻從來都不曾知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:50.49,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這絲線將通向何處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:51.42,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(僅僅佇立於此)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:54.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}每當我與他人分享
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:58.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}靈感乍現時的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.53,0:23:02.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就已經隱約察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:05.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終會有結束的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:09.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}重置人生的那扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:13.36,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終有漸漸打開之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:17.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}美好時光關入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:20.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}再慢慢地沉入湖底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:24.71,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不過我會在星星上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.93,0:23:30.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}寫下一句「我沒事」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經不能再在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟以前的那個時候一樣  大家一起來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和大家都等著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五個人聚在一起的話  一定會成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.35,0:00:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著妳
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:09.94,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,460)\pos(45,270)}「再見的意義」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  跟汐音發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天還以為已經和好如初了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經說了要和我一起做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戶川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她又想不開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說些什麼呢  汐音只是很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡面是很想在一起的  只是害羞不敢說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  不要亂說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是直接去問過的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「妳是喜歡還是討厭乃乃香  說清楚啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真能問得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那還用說嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以乃乃香  期待著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  我相信汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  沒有跟乃乃香她們在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾  我有件事情想問妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望實現之後  飛碟會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望實現之後  又會被新的願望召喚而去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟被大家召喚過來的時候是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「飛碟  飛碟」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「拜託你  實現我的願望吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就可以實現乃乃香和汐音的願望了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  就回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星象儀  諾艾爾也會去看的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  給我入場券吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是飛碟沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒關係啦  所以諾艾爾也要去看星象儀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾  汐音也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣大家都會笑開懷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳  諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北美祭  週日我大概會去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備還順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有點遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有三天  必須趕快做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被小春哭著說「這樣子一定趕不上了」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是為了饅頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實也是人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不早說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西四個人怎麼做的來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣應該就能趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說妳也來幹活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不發出指示的話  大家怎麼知道自己要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  就算沒有妳的指示  大家也能好好幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也快去動手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼啊  一副自以為是的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  汐音的話一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的小春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音一定會來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她和大家一樣  也給了諾艾爾入場券
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以汐音也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定要讓它成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發生讓爸爸擔心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是希望儘快去你那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  明明是自己說要留下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經在下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天啊  真是一轉眼的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  會來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然啊  不會有錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家聚在一起  又像過去一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用小春的饅頭慶祝圓滿成功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不關好門  全都看光了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湊太  過來  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(528,168,528,-10)\1c000000\bord0\frz-9}星象儀展示中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(148,75,148,-103)\1c000000\bord0\frz5.8}這裡是星象儀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到柚季的興趣也有發揮作用的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聚在一起的話  這麼多才夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  相信我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書上寫的東西  誰也沒有認真聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音相信的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不止我們兩個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人悄悄在商量什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想要拜託大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來召喚飛碟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:10:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟啊  真的來了的話真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定會嚇一跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會上電視呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春  柚季  湊太都笑得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音也會變得開心起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是大家的願望
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單過頭了吧  有點無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個必須的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼喚飛碟的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定要懷著某種願望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:10:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  就能引發很強的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟就會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  許願就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說飛碟會幫助我們實現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是願望有很多很多的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選其中一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥這個吝嗇鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為許下的願望要是跟別人說了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有可能實現不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不想要那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟  飛碟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現我的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:11:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的真是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她約好在這裡等的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香帶諾艾爾去逛一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的工作就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到汐音的話  就立刻聯繫妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會拿著這個在校舍裡繞繞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞起來好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(332,33)\1c000000\bord0\frz-21\fs20}年糕小豆湯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要試一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是豆沙包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是甜的  吃起來暖洋洋的  很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  乃乃香  汐音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該已經來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是去了星象儀那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完後  我們先回去柚季那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星象儀在這邊的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢慢欣賞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還沒到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北美祭才剛剛開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定會過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古宮也在嗎  來的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我向老師打聽了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戶川今天缺席了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾妳在這裡等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一趟汐音家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道地址嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香她們回來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去看看星象儀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和大家一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過一會大家就會來齊的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  跑得太快了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  誰叫妳帶著這玩意去追她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戶川的住址  我用郵件發給她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我應該往哪邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  妳現在在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才看見她了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本想告訴妳不要接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不去北美祭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是我沒講清楚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不想和你們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為不原諒我所以才不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳等了七年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道不能讓妳馬上會原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我對汐音妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是笨蛋嗎  我不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽到妳的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再對我說無謂的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾也在等著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳把票送給她  其實是想和她一起看的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和大家  和諾艾爾一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起看星象儀  一起看流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和過去一樣  和大家一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起聊天  一起歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一副親暱的模樣  叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說出來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再稱呼妳「戶川同學」了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再看到妳  不想再聽到妳的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想和妳成為什麼好友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能再笑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到  諾艾爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和妳不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會做出無法兌現的諾言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會讓他人去期待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  古宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香找到汐音了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  五人不聚在一起的話  不就沒意義了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們過來幫忙收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.41,0:20:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  收拾的活就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾的話就交給我們處理就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特意讓你們過來了  真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不可以放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  諾艾爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才明明還在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追乃乃香了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去找一下她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.29,0:21:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
